<br>
/shield lasts 15 seconds with a 3 minute refresh time. Person being shielded takes 50% of the damage and the warrior using /shield takes 75% - mob does 125% damage total.<br>
<br>
Warriors using a shield in their off hand will actually have higher damage mitigation when /shield is activated....wow actually thought out!<br>
